out actual code is in main/master branch
soo to copy the code in staging
we create staging branch by writing git branch staging
then we create feature branch and make changes in that whatever we wnt to do
some companies make one more copy develop and test all the changes of all works fine
if yes then feature merge to staging and staging merge to feature


to make new branch ----------git branch staging
to go to that branch --------git checkout staging
to create and change branch ------git checkout -b staging


